                    TECHNO BAZAAR (Sell!!! Sell!! Sell!)
                  </p>
                </div>
                <div class="card-inner">
                  <section class="content-inner">
                    <h2 class="content-sub-heading">
                      TECHNO BAZAAR (Sell!!! Sell!! Sell!)
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                      <a class="btn collapsed waves-attach waves-button"
                      data-toggle="collapse" href=
                      "cs#collapsible-region-1"><span class=
											"collapsed-hide"><i class="fa fa-eye-slash"></i> hide</span><span class=
											"collapsed-show"><i class="fa fa-eye"></i> view</span></a>
                    </p>
                    <div class="collapsible-region collapse" id=
                    "collapsible-region-1">
                      <div>
                        
                        <p></p>
                        <p id="rules">
                          Rules
                        </p>1.Each team should contain2-3 members.<br>
                        2. Each team should bring smart phones with internet
                        connection and dubsmash app installed.<br>
                        3.Reporting time .11:45 am<br>
                        <br>
                        PRELIMS<br>
                        <br>
                        Dubsmash<br>
                        1. 2 to 3 participants should participate for this
                        round.<br>
                        2. Each team will be provided with an audio sample
                        which is of 30 to 45 seconds.<br>
                        3. The team should perform the Dubsmash for their
                        provided audio when they are called.<br>
                        4. Points will be valued based on their expression,
                        body language and mouth movement to their respective
                        audio.<br>
                        5. Judges decision is final.<br>
                        <br>
                        SEMIFINALS<br>
                        <br>
                        Designing Skills<br>
                        1. In this round the teams are supposed to present a
                        poster for the product which they are allotted.<br>
                        2. Gimp will be provided at the venue.<br>
                        3. No other external software other than those provided
                        by the coordinators will be allowed.<br>
                        4. No internet access or external plugins will be
                        provided.<br>
                        5. Judging will be thoroughly based on the Quality,
                        Creativity and Perfection.<br>
                        6. Decision of Judges shall be final.<br>
                        7. Poor images will be declared as Invalid entry.<br>
                        <br>
                        FINALS<br>
                        <br>
                        Adzap<br>
                        1. Each team will be given a Technical product
                        name.<br>
                        2. The team should perform Adzap for their given
                        product for 3 to 5 minutes.<br>
                        3. Product name and Tag line should be mentioned during
                        performance.<br>
                        4. Usage of Mobiles by the team during the event will
                        lead to elimination<br>
                        5. The performance must be decent with no vulgar
                        act.<br>
                        6. The performance is Judged based on the clarity
                        thought, innovativeness, humor, team co-ordination and
                        expression.
                        <p></p>
                        <p></p>
                        <p id="prize">
                          Prize
                        </p>FIRST PRIZE : Rs. 5000<br>
                        SECOND PRIZE : Rs. 3000<br>
                        THIRD PRIZE : Rs. 1000
                        <p></p>
