                    "collapsible-region-2">
                      <div>
                        
                        <p></p>
                        <p id="rules">
                          Rules
                        </p>1. The programme consist of two sections.<br>
                        2. The first section is the priliminary test and the
                        second section is the coding section.<br>
                        3. The team has to pass the priliminary test to qualify
                        for the second section.<br>
                        4. Each team should contain only two members.<br>
                        <br>
                        Rules for coding section:<br>
                        <br>
                        1. Time alloted for each question is 30 minutes.<br>
                        2. The first member of the team has to start coding the
                        program, and the second member should wait outside.<br>
                        3. After 15 minutes the second member has to come in
                        and the first member has to go out.<br>
                        4. Communication between the team members are not
                        allowed.<br>
                        5. Comments are not allowed in the program code.<br>
                        6. Decisions made by the programme coordinators will be
                        the final.
                        <p></p>
                        <p></p>
