                        <p></p>
                        <p id="rules">
                          Rules
                        </p>1. Participants are requested to mail the abstract
                        along with their paper and contact details on or before
                        20th September, 2015 to csit.bodhi2015@vjcet.org.<br>
                        2. Confirmed list of papers selected for presentation
                        will be announced on 21st September, 2015.<br>
                        3. The candidates should send their name, phone number,
                        email id, and the name of the college along with the
                        paper.<br>
                        4. Details regarding the registration fee are published
                        in the main page.<br>
                        5. Maximum participation of two members in a group is
                        allowed.<br>
                        6. The participants are requested to report at the
                        registration desk 30minutes before the commencement of
                        the event.<br>
                        7. Participants should bring three hard copies of their
                        paper with them.<br>
                        9. The hard copies and presentation slides bought are
                        to be submitted at the time of registration.<br>
                        10. A session of 15min for presentation & another of
                        5min for queries will be provided for each
                        candidate.<br>
                        11. Accessories like projector, laptop, etc. will be
                        provided.<br>
                        12. Decision of judges will be final.<br>
                        13. Directions provided by the coordinators should be
                        strictly adhered to.
                        <p></p>
